      </div>
      <p class="section-lead" style="max-width:65ch;">This Agreement governs the relationship between Sentinel Authority (&ldquo;SA&rdquo;) and organizations seeking ODD Conformance Determination (ODDC) for autonomous systems.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 var(--space-2);">

      <!-- Critical Understanding -->
      <div class="hud-frame hud-frame-red hud-scanline"><i></i>
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:12px;">
