          <span class="hud-dot hud-dot-red"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="hud-desc" style="margin-bottom:12px;">ODDC attests that a system operates within defined boundaries with non-bypassable enforcement at the time of determination.</div>
        <div class="hud-label" style="margin-bottom:8px;color:rgba(220,53,69,0.7);">ODDC IS NOT</div>
        <div class="hud-row" style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;"><span class="hud-dot hud-dot-red" style="margin-top:5px;"></span><span class="hud-desc">Regulatory approval, safety attestation, product attestation</span></div>
        <div class="hud-row" style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;"><span class="hud-dot hud-dot-red" style="margin-top:5px;"></span><span class="hud-desc">Guarantee of performance, insurance, or warranty</span></div>
        <div class="hud-row" style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;"><span class="hud-dot hud-dot-red" style="margin-top:5px;"></span><span class="hud-desc">Applicant remains solely responsible for system behavior and all consequences of operation</span></div>
      </div>

