        <div class="hud-desc" style="margin-bottom:12px;">SA will evaluate and determine conformance based on:</div>
        <div class="hud-row" style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;"><span class="hud-dot hud-dot-green" style="margin-top:5px;"></span><div><span class="hud-title" style="font-size:12px;">ODD Specification</span><div class="hud-desc">The Operational Design Domain as specified by Applicant</div></div></div>
